file_content.text: That Imperial slimeball got what he deserved. Good riddance.
I'll escort our guest to his holding cell myself. You'd better meet the general.
We're right behind you.
You made it! We thought the major was kidding when he told us you were taking the front by yourselves.
Glad to see you made it through in one piece, Master Jedi!
Captain! Good to see you! I wasn't sure that even Havoc Squad could plow through the guards at the front and come out alive.
I can't believe you survived that gauntlet! Are you made of durasteel?
I'm impressed. I didn't think anyone could make a frontal assault on this place.
Glad you made it through. The front doors were brutal. We lost a lot of good men.
The front entrance is secured, Master Jedi. My squad took a beating--we lost some good men, but we're ready to fight.
Red Squad reporting for duty, Captain. We took a pounding coming through the front, but we're ready for some payback.
Glad you made it! Our squad took heavy casualties, but we're ready for action.
You made it! Good! We lost some of our people in the assault on the doors. My squad's itching to make some Imperials pay.
There's bound to be trouble up ahead.
I'll take point. Let's go find Moff Dracen.
Stay behind me.
No need for alarm, Captain. Just follow me, and we'll be fine.
The Force is with us.
Havoc Squad deals with worse than this before breakfast every day. Let's get moving.
It's not that bad.
Story of my life. Always someone lurking, waiting to kill you. You get used to it.
There's always trouble ahead.
Let's fight some Imperials.
You heard the order, men! Move out!
